description:
If you're looking for a violent game where you try to kill as many things as you can, you've come to the wrong place. These shapes mostly look like polygons. Some of the animations are incredible. Gameplay is enjoyable.

My biggest complaint is that there are only three levels. Once you've gone through all of the levels a couple times, you are pretty much good enough to master them all pretty quickly.
summary: Quite a unique program - would not call a shooter
